==Korean==
===Noun===
'''채'''
#A whip
#:팽이를 '''채'''로 치다. (He) hits the spinning top with a whip. 
#Counter for houses:
#:집 한 '''채''' One house.
#A thin strip
#:무우를 '''채'''를 치다. Cut [[white radish]] into thin strips.
#A continuing state
#:옷을 입은 '''채'''. while wearing clothes / without undressing
#A Korean family name (hanja:[[菜]])
===Adverb===
'''채'''
#Not yet, still... not
#:숙제를 '''채''' 마치기도 전에 잠이 들었다. He fell asleep before he finished the homework.

